{"tid":1581887,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉]For admin, 有關防fake news做法","createTime":"2019-09-19T19:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T19:03:26.000Z","uid":119950,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"54ca3db38c8e98d3bc3dd7380c3dfb418f839308","tid":1581887,"uid":119950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T19:15:01.000Z","msg":"有見最近愈黎愈多、愈黎愈密既fake news出現<br />\n個人建議連仔可以設定USER係每篇新文章留言預切&quot;不推文回覆&quot;為開<br />\n以防其他USER一睇到就衝留言推起哂D post<br />\n<br />\n同埋針對成日放fake news既USER進行調查<br />\n甚或暫時禁言<br />\n<br />\n只係簡單brainstorm, 都知有言論自由同少少邏輯問題<br />\n但fake news真係愈黎愈嚴重<br />\n我都只能盡快拋磚引新方法解決件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1edbd48c01dc47bc5e3835754038e510c57769","tid":1581887,"uid":155107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T19:16:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">fake news = 5毛<br />\n見一隻扑一隻</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b7b35dee2c221e456322bb512e350fc06dafe647","tid":1581887,"uid":119950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a1edbd48c01dc47bc5e3835754038e510c57769","tid":1581887,"uid":155107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T19:16:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">fake news = 5毛<br />\n見一隻扑一隻</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T19:31:29.000Z","msg":"但要考慮埋好多user都唔block/懶得block既情況<br />\n唔係個個都會向下睇d comment再諗係咪fake news"},{"pid":"c99c363e41dc67fcba283d13acedf2d0c9ef27b3","tid":1581887,"uid":74182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T20:12:59.000Z","msg":"有個方法唔知可唔可行<br />\n係每個post 加個fake news 制比人投<br />\n次數有限，例如每人只限投一次同埋可能P牌冇得投<br />\n累積夠某個數量就會自動del post, <br />\n但呢個方法行得通係建基於正常人多過五毛<br />\n唔係就好易比對家利用返個基制"},{"pid":"9079333cff08cbfebd44e56215c09782a7c09014","tid":1581887,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09